and blessings be upon you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap par ay Abbas ibne Abdul Muttalib. Salaam ho aap par ay Rasool'e Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke chacha. Salaam ho aap par ay Saheb'e Saqqah (paani pilaane waale) aur Allah ki rehmat aur barkat ho aap par.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو آپ پر اے عباس ابن عبد المطلب، سلام ہو آپ پر اے رسول اللہؐ کے چچا، سلام ہو آپ پر اے صاحبِ سقایتہ (پانی پلانے والے) اور اللہ کی رحمت اور برکت ہو۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA A’BBAASUBNO A’BDIL MUTTALEBE. ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA A’MMA RASOOLIL LAAHE. ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA SAAHEBAS SEQAAYATE WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا عَبَّاسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْمُطَّلِبِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا عَمَّ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا صَاحِبَ السِّقَایَۃِ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, 