ALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA A’MMA HABEE-BAL-LAAH. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA A’MMAL MUSTAFAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA SAYYEDA-NAL IMAA-MUL HASANUL MUJTABAA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA SAYYDA-NAL IMAAMO ZAIY-NUL-A’A-BE-DEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَنَا یَا عَبَّاسُ یَا عَمَّ رَسُوْلَ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا عَمَّ نَبِیِّ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا عَمَّ حَبِیْبَ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا عَمَّ الْمُصْطَفٰی۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَنَا الْاِمَامُ الْحَسَنُ الْمُجْتَبٰی۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَنَا الْاِمَامُ زَیْنُ الْعَابِدِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1017532, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap par ay hamare sayyad o sardaar Imam Baqir. Salaam ho aap par ay hamare sayyad o sardaar Imam Jafar Sadiq, ay ahlebait’e nabuwwat, ay ma’dan’e risaalat, aap hazraat par salaam ho, Khuda aap hazraat se raazi ho aur aap hazraat ko apni behtareen raza se raazi kare aur Jannat aap hazraat ka marqaz o maskan aur mahel'e nuzool wa thikaana qaraar de. Aap hazraat par salaam ho aur Allah ki rehmat o barkat ho.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو آپ پر اے ہمارے سید و سردار امام باقر، سلام ہو آپ پر اے ہمارے سید و سردار امام جعفر صادقؑ، اے اہلبیت نبوت، اے معدنِ رسالت، آپ حضرات پر سلام ہو، خدا آپ حضرات سے راضی ہو اور آپ حضرات کو اپنی بہیترین رضا سے راضی کرے اور جنّت آپ حضرات کا مرقد و مسکن اور محل نزدل و ٹھکانہ قرار دے، آپ حضرات پر سلام ہو اور اللہ کی رحمت و برکت ہو۔ ", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA SAYYADA-NAL IMAA-MUL BAAQE-RO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KA YAA SAYYADA-NAL IMAAMO JA’FA-ROO-NIS-SAADE-QO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KUM YAA AHLA-BAIY-TUN NABOO-WATE WA MA’DE-NAR-RESAA-LATE-RAZE-YAL-LAAHO A’N-KUM WA AR-ZAA-KUM AH-SANAR REZAA, WA JA-A’LAL JANNATA MASWAA-KUM WA MASKANA-KUM WA MAHALLA-KUM WA MAAWAA-LUM. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIY-KUM WA RAHMA-TUL-LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَنَا الْاِمَامُ الْبَاقِرُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَنَا الْاِمَامُ جَعْفَرٌ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "الصَّدِقُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ یَآ اَهْلَ بَیْتُ النُّبُوَّۃِ وَمَعْدِنَ الرِّسَالَۃِ رَضِیَ اللهُ عَنْكُمْ وَاَرْضَاكُمْ اَحْسَنَ الرِّضَا، وَجَعَلَ الْجَنَّۃَ مَثْوٰیكُمْ وَمَسْكَنَكُمْ وَمَحَلَّكُمْ وَمَاوٰیكُمْ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ وَرَحَمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": nu